pull.title: txmempool: Remove unused default value MemPoolRemovalReason::UNKNOWN
pull.body: The `remove*` methods set the removal reason to `UNKNOWN` by default. This is nowhere used; Except in tests, where the value doesn't matter. Fix that by removing the confusing default.
